result.text:
When meeting with Secretary Raimondo on Aug. 29, Premier Li Qiang noted that China-US economic and trade ties are win-win in nature. Politicizing economic and trade issues and overstretching the concept of security will seriously undermine bilateral relations and mutual trust, damage the interests of enterprises and people of both countries, and have a disastrous impact on the global economy.
He called on the two sides to enhance mutually beneficial cooperation, reduce friction and confrontation, and jointly promote global recovery and combat global challenges.
